title: The Who 2016-02-27 Joe Louis Arena, Detroit
description:
Here is a fresh bootleg. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

Who Are You

This was shot from side stage.  
Started out great for the first 
hour but fans got restless and 
wanted to dance a few rows in 
front of me.  Constantly sitting 
and standing and tons of people 
making beer runs and bathroom breaks.  
It's just one of those things I can't 
control.  Video turned out quite well 
although not as good as my Columbus 
Who video.  I wanted to get this up 
before I leave on vacation tomorrow 
as I will be gone for almost 3 weeks.  
I obviously didn't watch this show 
a second time yet so I don't believe 
any problems except what I mentioned 
allready.  As always with any of my videos.  
Please do what you want with them, 
share them, edit them, dub them or whatever.  
Enjoy!!
